Line 135 in `bin.py` https://github.com/jorgebastida/awslogs/blob/master/awslogs/bin.py#L135 is misspelled:

    if options.aws_profile:
        os.environ['AWS_PROFILE'] = option.aws_profile

As there is no variable `option`, it would fail. It shall read:

    if options.aws_profile:
        os.environ['AWS_PROFILE'] = options.aws_profile

